#!/bin/bash
# Colors for Style
GREEN='\033[0;32m'
RED='\033[0;31m'
CYAN='\033[0;36m'
YELLOW='\033[1;33m'
NC='\033[0m'

clear
echo -e "${GREEN}"
echo "  ZZZZZZ   AAAAA  IIIII  N   N "
echo "      Z   A     A   I    NN  N "
echo "     Z    AAAAAAA   I    N N N "
echo "    Z     A     A   I    N  NN "
echo "  ZZZZZZ  A     A  IIIII  N   N "
echo -e "${NC}"

echo -e "${CYAN}--- WELCOME TO ZAIN MATRIX SUITE ---${NC}"
echo -e "${YELLOW}1)${NC} Show System Dashboard (Old Tool)"
echo -e "${YELLOW}2)${NC} Matrix Rain Effect (Cool Look)"
echo -e "${YELLOW}3)${NC} Fake Hacking Animation"
echo -e "${YELLOW}4)${NC} Exit"
echo ""
read -p "Chose an option: " choice

if [ $choice -eq 1 ]; then
    Zain # Aapka purana tool chal jayega
elif [ $choice -eq 2 ]; then
    pkg install cmatrix -y && cmatrix
elif [ $choice -eq 3 ]; then
    echo -e "${RED}Accessing Satellite...${NC}"
    sleep 1
    echo -e "${YELLOW}Bypassing Firewall... 25%${NC}"
    sleep 1
    echo -e "${YELLOW}Extracting Data... 75%${NC}"
    sleep 1
    echo -e "${GREEN}SUCCESS! System Controlled.${NC}"
elif [ $choice -eq 4 ]; then
    exit
else
    echo "Invalid Choice!"
fi
